data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful and peaceful retreat nestled in the heart of Windmill Woods! This stunning new 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home is located on a desirable corner lot, providing ample privacy and tranquility.

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting open floor plan that seamlessly flows from the large living room to the elegant kitchen and dining area, perfect for entertaining family and friends. The master suite boasts a peaceful and serene ambiance, allowing you to escape the hustle and bustle of everyday life.

One of the most attractive features of this home is its location. Windmill Woods is a wooded community that offers a serene and peaceful environment. You'll love the quiet surroundings and the absence of neighbors across the street, ensuring maximum privacy and tranquility.

The location is also highly desirable due to its proximity to unique beach shopping, dining, and world-class beach activities, all just a short walk away. With Bethany Beach and Quiet Resorts less than 3 miles away, you can enjoy the beauty of the ocean every day.

This single-family ranch style home features a 2-car garage and has no children living in the home, making it an ideal location for a peaceful and quiet lifestyle. You'll love the abundance of fine dining and beach activities in the area, and the safe and peaceful environment ensures a worry-free living experience.

Come and experience the beauty and tranquility of this amazing home in Windmill Woods. It's the perfect place to call home!
data.whatILove:
For starters, the proximity to the beach and ocean is a significant draw for many people. There's something special about being close to the water, with the sound of the waves lulling you to sleep at night and the salt air invigorating your senses in the morning.

Additionally, living in a home in Windmill Woods offers the perfect balance of tranquility and convenience. The peaceful wooded community provides a serene atmosphere where you can relax and unwind, while still being just a short walk away from shopping, dining, and beach activities.

Your home's open floor plan and spacious living areas are ideal for hosting gatherings with friends and family, creating cherished memories that will last a lifetime. And with the master suite providing a peaceful retreat from the world, you can recharge and rejuvenate whenever you need it.

Overall, living at the beach in a beautiful home like yours offers the best of both worlds – the tranquility of a peaceful community and the excitement of endless beach activities and entertainment.
